<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>50 Albemarle St.</placeName><!-- Begin each line with <lb/> as here -->
<lb/><date when="1858-01-08">8 August
<lb/>1858</date></dateline><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Sir</salute></opener><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p><space extent="8" unit="chars"/>I am really quite
<lb/>ashamed to find that so much
<lb/>time has glided away since
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I received your most kind 
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>and liberal present of books 
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>and no acknowledgement 
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>been made, I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> stand
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><unclear cert="low">listening</unclear> well you see
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>it makes me forget
                
                <pb facs="liv_001172_0002" n="0002"/>
                
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>my best friends and I suppose 
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>some of them will be saying
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I have "forgotten myself."
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>So many things have occupied
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>my attention of late that
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>time speeds on more swiftly
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>than ever it did. Indeed
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>one has scarcely time to
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>think in this whirl and
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>glad I shall be if I again
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>get a little time in Africa
    <lb/>to think. I beg you will
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>forgive my long silence.
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I went down to Scotland
                
                <pb facs="liv_001172_0003" n="0003"/>
    <lb/>to spend Christmas and New 
    <lb/><choice><orig>yearsday</orig><reg>Year's Day</reg></choice> and have neglected 
    <lb/>many duties in consequence
    <lb/>none of which I regret more
    <lb/>than that <add place="above">which made me</add>
    <del type="strikethrough">of</del> appear<del type="strikethrough">ing</del>
    <unclear cert="low">mutinous</unclear>
    <lb/>in gratitude to you for your 
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>liberality. I return you my
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>warmest thanks for the
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>books and feel most
    <lb/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>grateful for the kind
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>sentences which <w>accom<supplied>-</supplied>
        <lb break="no"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>-panied</w> them. May our
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>heavenly Father abundantly
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>reward you for all your
    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>kindly feelings.</p>
    
    <pb facs="liv_001172_0004" n="0004"/>
                <lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>Please present my
                    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>kindest salutations to your
                    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>family nephew for
                    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I suppose your brother's
                    <lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>children stay with you
        <lb/><space extent="5" unit="chars"/>hoping you are
                    <lb/> of a forgiving dispostion
                </p>
                <lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><closer><salute>I am truly + gratefully</salute><!-- Change as appropriate -->
                    <lb/><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>yours
            <lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>
        
    
                
                
        



